As for my reasons that a fetus (3+ months in womb) is a person, here are the basics: Just like an infant, it has a beating heart has a brain with detectable brainwaves has eyes has arms, hands, fingers, legs, feet, toes has all organs responds to sound, light, movements, pressure actually “looks” like a humanBy the 4th month of pregnancy, there is no mistaking that what is growing inside the mother is alive and has countless attributes of a person.
